collectionMetadata.name: Enrolment - Pre-University, By Level and Course
collectionMetadata.description: Since 2006, as part of a new broad-based JC education, students are required to do at least one subject outside their area of specialization. For example, a Science course student is required to take at least one Humanities subject and an Arts course student is required to take at least one Science subject.
